cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper focuses on graph classification using Graph Neural Networks (GNNs) and meta-learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper utilizes reinforcement learning, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with image classification, which is a sub-topic of computer vision, hence cs.CV (Computer Vision) is another likely sub-category. The paper also mentions natural language processing, which falls under cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the paper uses neural networks, which is a sub-topic of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
